# Calendar API — separate app

- **`Calendar API/` is not part of REACT-ADMIN.** It is a standalone Google Apps Script project kept in the workspace for reference and local editing only.
- **Do not** `git add`, commit, or push the `Calendar API/` directory. It is listed in `.gitignore`.
- When changing GAS behavior, edit files under `Calendar API/` as needed, but **remind the user** to copy changes into their Apps Script project and deploy from the GAS editor (this folder is not versioned with the main app).
